reviewText: Not a fan.  My grandchildren were not impressed.  (2 years)
Fun show, clean and great for kids.
Meet my expectations just like quileys village from my childhood and my brother loved it too.

This is a wonderful Christian show for children. The puppets are precious and Mr. Quigley is like a Mr. Rogers.
I highly recommend!
i love Quigley's Village stories and songs. my cousin is 3 years old, and she enjoys watching the stories before bedtime. i wish to have all the videos. thanks, clara
